Behavioral / Situational Questions (Accenture focuses on these)

Describe a situation where you handled a conflict in your team.

Explain a time when you failed. What did you learn?

Tell me about a time when you managed multiple tasks under pressure.

Describe a time when you had to learn something quickly.

Tell me about a situation where you took initiative.

How do you handle stress or deadlines?

How do you prioritize your work?

Describe a time you helped a teammate.

What motivates you?

How do you respond to criticism?
